armor, FIRE BREATH 🔥🔥🔥.<br></li><li><strong>Terrifying robotic enemies</strong> that actually get pretty hard! Sword robots, bow robots, Spidertron 5000, Spidertron 6000, gigantic hammer bots. So many things to dismember.<br></li><li><strong>Level Editor: </strong>Make custom levels and challenges and share them with other humans! Explore the rich Workshop library of awesome human-built levels!<br></li><li><strong>Achievements! </strong>Unlock upgrades, emotes and multiplayer skins by achieving a rich variety of things!<br></li><li><strong>Emotes!</strong> Do the Funky Pillar Dance, mock your foes, or flap your arms delightfully!</li></ul>",
